Package example.managers

Class MyLinkedList

java.lang.Object
example.managers.MyLinkedList
All Implemented Interfaces:
Iterable<SpaceMarine>
public class MyLinkedList extends Object implements Iterable<SpaceMarine>
The MyLinkedList class represents a linked list of SpaceMarine objects. Implements the Iterable interface for the ability to iterate over the elements of the list.
